<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
    <head>
      <meta charset="utf-8">
      <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
        <title>MyStudy planner</title>
        <link rel="manifest" href="../site.webmanifest">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap-grid.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap-utilities.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap-grid.rtl.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white fixed-top">
        <img class="flex" src="immagini/logo.jpg" alt="">
        <h1><font color="black">MyStudy planner</font></h1> 
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent" aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
          <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
          <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <div><br></div>
      <div><br></div>
      <div class="grid">
      <div><br></div>
      <div><br></div>
      <div class="position-relative vert">
        <div align = "center">
        <div class="titlegrid">
          <form method="post">
            <input type="email" placeholder="E-mail" aria-label="mail" name="inputEmail" required>
            <div><br></div>
            <input type="password" placeholder="Password" aria-label="password" name="pass" required>
            <div><br></div>
            <button class="btn my-2 my-sm-0 btncolor mr-sm-2" type="submit" name="loginButton">Login</button>
            <div><br></div>
          </form>
          <!--modifica testo-->
            <div class="testo position-relative center-50 start-0" style="padding-left: 30px; padding-right: 30px;"><strong><font color="black" size="2">Vuoi pianificare le tue giornate di studio?<br>MyStudy planner è la tua soluzione!</font></strong></div>
          </div>
          <div class="position-relative vert2"> 
            <button class="btn my-2 my-sm-0 btncolor mr-sm-2 position-relative" type="submit" style="align-items: center;">Registrati</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <div class="secondgrid row">
          <div class="card col-lg-4">
            <img src="immagini/img1.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Problemi a pianificare il tuo studio?</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Se vuoi organizzarti al meglio per evitare di fare confusione<br>Utilizza MyStudy</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card col-lg-4">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="img2.png" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Migliaia di libri e appunti</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Puoi caricare i tuoi apunti per averli tutti nello stesso posto<br>Puoi cercare i testi di cui hai bisogno</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card col-lg-4">
            <img src="immagini/img3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Accedi al tuo calendario</h5>
              <p class="card-text">MyStudy ti aiuterà a pianificare le tue giornate al meglio</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </body>
</html>